\subsection{Rejection Sampling}
\label{sec:rejection_sampling}

Following the setup in \citet{webgpt}, we performed rejection sampling by generating 16 completions for each of the 300 prompts in the human preference annotation test set. We set the temperature to 0.9 and computed best-of-$n$ for $n \in \{1, 2, 4, 6, 8, 16\}$. Completions were generated using GPT-5 and Gemini-2.5-Pro.

